### A Note to Users

While you're free to copy, modify, and redistribute this code, we encourage you to:
1. Reference the official NuGet packages for ease of use and to stay up-to-date.
2. Contribute back to the project by submitting issues, suggestions, or pull requests on GitHub.

Your engagement helps improve the library for everyone!
